---
import { site } from "@/data/site";
import { withBase } from "@/lib/path";
---

<section class="relative isolate overflow-hidden bg-white" data-vision-hero>
  <div class="container-page bg-white pb-20 pt-0">
    <div class="relative isolate min-h-[440px] overflow-hidden bg-slate-900 sm:min-h-[520px] lg:min-h-[620px]">
      <img
        class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover object-[58%_48%]"
        src={withBase("/images/home-hero-family.png")}
        alt="푸른 공원에서 건강한 일상을 보내는 가족 이미지"
        loading="eager"
        decoding="async"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/28"></div>
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_center,rgba(11,31,51,0.18),rgba(11,31,51,0.58))]"></div>
      <div class="relative flex min-h-[440px] items-center justify-center px-6 py-20 text-center text-white sm:min-h-[520px] lg:min-h-[620px]">
        <div class="max-w-4xl [text-shadow:0_3px_18px_rgba(0,0,0,0.42)]">
          <p class="mb-5 text-sm font-black tracking-[0.34em] text-emerald-100">VISION OF BIOLAB</p>
          <h1 class="text-6xl font-light tracking-[0.02em] sm:text-7xl lg:text-8xl">
            {site.englishName}
          </h1>
          <p class="mt-7 text-lg font-bold leading-8 text-white sm:text-xl">
            건강기능식품과 이너케어 브랜드로 건강한 일상의 기준을 만듭니다.
          </p>
          <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-2xl text-sm font-semibold leading-7 text-white/88 sm:text-base">
            비오랩은 여성과 아이의 건강을 위한 원료, 제품, 유통 경험을 연구합니다.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
